	<presentation id="index">
		<title>Creating the Composable Enterprise</title>
		<toc class="abstract">Digital transformation not only requires a specific focus on digital opportunities, it also requires the ability to adapt and change easily. Managing everything as a building block makes every capability easily usable and reusable. In a digital world, building blocks become digital building blocks, and all capabilities of an enterprise should be managed as digital building blocks.</toc>
